title: Ethiopia: Home of Humankind
author: Clariss39
pages:
Ethopia (where we arw
now) is a place where
some of the oldest
skeletal evidence of
homo sapiens have
been found! It is also
theorized to be the
region from where the
first humans set out
to the Middle East and
beyond. This makes it
the cradle of mankind.
